-- ============================================================
-- CookingServer — Script
-- Location: ServerScriptService
--
-- Owns the two-station cooking pipeline (Part 10 / Part 41A):
--   PREP TABLE  (attribute IsPrep=true)  → ingredient assembly → Uncooked dish
--   STOVETOP    (attribute IsStovetop=true) → heat bar → Cooked / Burned dish
--
-- Remotes (auto-created if not in ChompersRemotes):
--   ShowPrepUI        Server→Client   Open prep panel with valid recipe list
--   HidePrepUI        Server→Client   Close prep panel
--   RequestAssemble   Client→Server   Player picks a recipe
--   AssembleResult    Server→Client   Success (dish data) or failure reason
--   ShowCookUI        Server→Client   Stovetop cook-timer starts
--   HideCookUI        Server→Client   Close stovetop panel
--   BeginHeatBar      Server→Client   Cook timer done — show heat bar
--   StopHeatBar       Client→Server   Player pressed E; sends needle position (0–1)
--   CookingComplete   Server→Client   Final cookStatus + cl modifier
--   SousChefJoin      Client→Server   Ally presses E at active station
--   SousChefAck       Server→Client   Confirm sous-chef registered
-- ============================================================

